{"tid":745617,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃浩控敵本土壹傳媒行政總裁誹謗","createTime":"2018-07-17T02:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T02:48:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5b042d7872d0eb38969514cc5bf7c45439031d3c","tid":745617,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T02:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180717/large/1531793810_1010.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180717%2Flarge%2F1531793810_1010.jpg&h=320a8772&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180717/large/1531793811_e968.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180717%2Flarge%2F1531793811_e968.jpg&h=6c6aade7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n壹傳媒有限公司行政總裁張劍虹 (盧峰?)<br />\n<br />\n壹傳媒擬將《壹週刊》業務出售予商人黃浩的交易今年2月告吹，壹傳媒行政總裁張劍虹早前接受《都巿日報》訪問時提及有關交易。由黃浩控制的買家公司日前入稟高院，指張的言論嚴重影響買家公司的聲譽，要求禁制張發表誹謗言論及索償。<br />\n<br />\n原告Gossip Daily Limited，被告為壹傳媒有限公司行政總裁及執行董事張劍虹。相關報道在本月3日於《都巿日報》刊登，報道聲稱張當時解釋交易不能成交的原因。原告認為張的說法令讀者以為是原告出錯令交易不能完成，說法嚴重傷害原告的聲譽。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀續指，張清楚知道原告已支付、賣家亦收妥8,800萬元，但張卻選擇隱瞞有關資料，不當地只交代事件中的部份內容。<br />\n<br />\n【案件編號：HCA1647/18】"},{"pid":"032c092ddcc696420310ff88d7b32f66f0d50959","tid":745617,"uid":158180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T02:44:00.000Z","msg":"都市日報本身就係錯洞嘅 用番佢報道內容告番人轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591db22138f952a74d9faf767584372395c2bcde","tid":745617,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T02:45:33.000Z","msg":"btw，張劍虹都抵撚死啦，佢上任總編之後蘋果衰曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e92ea55e0467700460815dc2e75091b2fdf9412","tid":745617,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi